{"talk":{"id":49424,"name":"Will Hurd: A wall won't solve America's border problems","description":"\"Building a 30-foot-high concrete structure from sea to shining sea is the most expensive and least effective way to do border security,\" says Congressman Will Hurd, a Republican from Texas whose district encompasses two times zones and shares an 820-mile border with Mexico. Speaking from Washington, DC in a video interview with former state attorney general Anne Milgram, Hurd discusses the US government's border policy and its controversial detention and child separation practices -- and lays out steps toward a better future at the border. (Recorded at the TED World Theater in New York on September 10, 2019)","slug":"will_hurd_a_wall_won_t_solve_america_s_border_problems","recorded_at":"2019-09-10 00:00:00","published_at":"2019-09-26 14:59:26","updated_at":"2020-09-28 21:41:41","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":621,"name":"TED Salon Border Stories"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/c736d336821d342b449595a1915c543f61f08469_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/c736d336821d342b449595a1915c543f61f08469_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/c736d336821d342b449595a1915c543f61f08469_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/c736d336821d342b449595a1915c543f61f08469_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/75dcb86aad3b99c388ea0be20431aff548072543_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/WillHurd_2019S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":8573754,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/WillHurd_2019S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":23799134,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"http